So, that's the phrase;

00:01:07.356 --> 00:01:10.056 A:middle
with great power comes
great responsibility.

00:01:11.276 --> 00:01:13.566 A:middle
And I learned that
phrase early on.

00:01:13.606 --> 00:01:17.426 A:middle
See, like the characters
I had moments in my life

00:01:17.426 --> 00:01:19.526 A:middle
that made me make decisions.

00:01:20.396 --> 00:01:23.326 A:middle
I was lucky, when I was very
young, when I was like four

