00:02:16.796 --> 00:02:18.046 A:middle
and I grabbed it,
and I bought it.

00:02:18.046 --> 00:02:23.166 A:middle
And I read that book over
and over and over again.

00:02:23.846 --> 00:02:26.716 A:middle
And it opened my eyes
to a whole new world.

00:02:26.846 --> 00:02:29.846 A:middle
It introduced me to
the Marvel Universe,

00:02:30.436 --> 00:02:32.676 A:middle
and from that moment
on I was hooked.

00:02:32.956 --> 00:02:34.836 A:middle
That was my thing, comic books.

00:02:35.226 --> 00:02:37.926 A:middle
And I was one of those crazy
kids who never stopped.

00:02:38.326 --> 00:02:41.606 A:middle
I read them through grade
school, through high school,

00:02:41.776 --> 00:02:43.546 A:middle
and even through college.

00:02:44.866 --> 00:02:49.236 A:middle
And I had a pretty good
collection until the summer

00:02:50.056 --> 00:02:53.346 A:middle
