00:07:06.736 --> 00:07:07.566 A:middle
and they turned him away.

00:07:08.066 --> 00:07:09.156 A:middle
They said he was too skinny.

00:07:09.156 --> 00:07:10.046 A:middle
He had flat feet.

00:07:10.166 --> 00:07:10.896 A:middle
They didn't want him.

00:07:11.786 --> 00:07:13.086 A:middle
But that did not
deter my friend.

00:07:13.086 --> 00:07:15.656 A:middle
He kept going to different
