00:07:20.166 --> 00:07:21.506 A:middle
and he went from one
recruitment office

00:07:21.506 --> 00:07:24.386 A:middle
to another collecting some
papers, and he saw my friend.

00:07:24.546 --> 00:07:27.846 A:middle
And he said, didn't I -- I just
saw that kid at the other place.

00:07:28.426 --> 00:07:30.986 A:middle
And he said, to his
fellow soldiers,

00:07:31.546 --> 00:07:32.536 A:middle
that's the guy we want.

00:07:33.456 --> 00:07:34.606 A:middle
And the other one said, him?

00:07:34.606 --> 00:07:35.276 A:middle
The skinny one?

00:07:35.276 --> 00:07:35.826 A:middle
And he said, yeah.

00:07:36.696 --> 00:07:39.666 A:middle
See, it's not about
this muscle right here,

00:07:39.886 --> 00:07:41.246 A:middle
it's about this muscle.

